{"title":"金字塔","authors":["蔡若秋"],"dates":[{"year":1991,"month":3,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"金字塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蔡若秋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九月，棉桃绽裂的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在棉田的绿色版面上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开出一篇篇爆炸性新闻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是梦还是现实"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖辈的经验是小秋收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小得如谷粒豆子高粱米"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如今旷野上白雾茫茫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花的海洋，把家乡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那载不动许多愁的小舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漂远了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是一场造山运动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花垛，让家乡的儿女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用汗水和双手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑成流金淌银的棉花山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遥望大田，辛勤的蜜蜂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍在花丛中采摘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一簇簇生活的蜜"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉花垛是故乡巍峨的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金字塔"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}